title: Beautiful South Austin Home Just a Short Walk to S Congress
posting_body: Stunning home available in a terrific location in South Austin now available.
Just a short walk to S Congress, and a bike ride to Zilker, the location couldn't be more central for 78704.

Built in 2019 and curated by 369 Development, Lucas Home Construction, Prospect Architecture, and SLIC interior design - Equipped with high-end appliances, walnut cabinets, imported tile, European white oak flooring, mid floor insulation, Anderson windows, custom closets, metal work and privacy landscaping
Pets negotiable, additional deposit required for approved pets
